title: Ep. 2824 - Tapu Sena's Prank - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 23 September 2019
shortDesc: Iyer, Babita, and Jethalal get their awards as well. The program is over and now everyone is back to their normal lives. Tapu Sena plays a prank with Bhide. Taarak and Anjali have a fun moment as well. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2825 - Vegetable Crisis - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 24 September 2019
shortDesc: There is a crisis of vegetables in Gokuldham society. The vegetable seller who usually comes hasn't been coming for the past few days. Every family is running out of vegetables. The women decide to go to the market when they see a little girl.

title: Ep. 2826 - Dr. Hathi's Good News - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 25 September 2019
shortDesc: The vegetable seller Sunita is sick and the Mahila Mandal is at her house. They call Dr. Hathi to check her. He tells them that she has a brain tumour and the operation will cost around three to four lakhs. He also gives them good news.

title: Ep. 2827 - Social Awareness - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 26 September 2019
shortDesc: Everyone is happy that Sunita was saved and she will be back to normal very soon. They are all very thankful for the Ayushman Bharat Yojna by the Indian Government. Every one of them plans to propagate the news of this scheme among the public.

title: Ep. 2828 - In The Middle Of A Riddle - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 27 September 2019
shortDesc: Everyone in the Gokuldham Society gets an old-school postcard. Each of these postcards has a riddle in them. All the families are trying to solve these riddles. They all want the prize promised to them on the postcard. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2829 -  The Unknown Gift - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 30 September 2019
shortDesc: Everybody in the Gokuldham receives a letter where it is written about some puzzle and the prize related to it. After that, everybody rushes to Taarak Mehta's house to find the solution but he is almost ready for office and he promises to solve it.

title: Ep. 2830 - Jethalal Gets Angry - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 1 October 2019
shortDesc: Fine morning, upon Jethalal's arrival he finds both Natu Kaka and Bagha absent in his shop. He immediately calls Bagha to comeback wherever he is. Meanwhile, Jethalal gets angry on both for their irresponsibility. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2831 - Puzzles Solved! - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 2 October 2019
shortDesc: Every member of the Gokuldham society reaches to Champaklal to solve their puzzle. And according to their expectations, he helps everyone in solving their puzzles. And in the end, they together celebrate Gandhi Jayanti. Stay tuned to know more!

title: Ep. 2832 - Gandhi Jayanti Program - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 3 October 2019
shortDesc: Gokuldham Society celebrates Gandhi Jayanti and they come onto the stage to perform. Jethalal brings on the starting performance and Sonu along with Tapu Sena performs a song in her angelic voice. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2833 - Knowing Gandhiji - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 4 October 2019
shortDesc: Champak Chacha and Bhide take Tapu Sena to the museum that is focused on Gandhiji and tells them that it was the home of Gandhiji. Tapu Sena learns a lot of things about Gandhiji and his life from the trip and there is a feeling of nationalism.

title: Ep. 2834 - Salsa Lessons For The Women - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 7 October 2019
shortDesc: The women in Gokuldham Society are learning salsa dance for the festival celebrations. They want to perform as well as Tapu Sena. On the other hand, they need help from Jethalal and Babita asks to meet. He gets a misconception and is excited to meet.

title: Ep. 2835 - Daya Is Missed - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 8 October 2019
shortDesc: Mahila Mandal comes to Jethalal and speaks about Daya. They all say that they miss Daya as Navratri is almost here. Speak of that Jethalal becomes emotional and he goes back home. He has a nostalgic evening. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2836 - Jethalal's Dream - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 9 October 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal dreams of Daya and is speaking in his sleep. When Champak Chacha comes to wake him up, Jethalal hurts his fingers. Popatlal has another heartbreak and the Navratri preparations have started. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2837 - Sundar Speaks To Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 10 October 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal wants to speak to Daya and hence calls her brother Sundar. Sundar speaks to him in Daya's voice. However, he gets caught and Jethalal is sad. Bhide calls a meeting for the Navratri celebrations. Stay tuned.

title: Ep. 2838 - Jethalal Has A Misconception - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 11 October 2019
shortDesc: Jetha doesn't attend the meeting he was about to and henceforth all the members reach him at his house to know the reason. He informs that he was afraid that he might get scolded by Bhide for being late.
